Files in this folder are based on libxml2-2.15.3

Upstream: https://gitlab.gnome.org/GNOME/libxml2
Tag:      v2.15.3

Layout
------
  src/            — library .c source files + internal headers (libxml.h,
                    timsort.h, config.h)
  include/libxml/ — public API headers + generated xmlversion.h
  include/private/ — private internal headers (new in libxml2 2.12+,
                     referenced as #include "private/foo.h" from source files)

config.h
--------
  Pre-configured for macOS ARM64 from config.h.cmake.in.
  Do not regenerate with cmake or autoconf; edit directly if platform
  feature flags need to change.

xmlversion.h
------------
  Generated from include/libxml/xmlversion.h.in with the following flags:
    WITH_THREADS=1, WITH_OUTPUT=1, WITH_PUSH=1, WITH_READER=1,
    WITH_PATTERN=1, WITH_WRITER=1, WITH_SAX1=1, WITH_HTTP=0 (stubs only),
    WITH_VALID=1, WITH_HTML=1, WITH_C14N=1, WITH_CATALOG=1,
    WITH_XPATH=1, WITH_XPTR=1, WITH_XINCLUDE=1,
    WITH_ICONV=0, WITH_ICU=0, WITH_ISO8859X=1, WITH_DEBUG=1,
    WITH_REGEXPS=1, WITH_RELAXNG=1, WITH_SCHEMAS=1, WITH_SCHEMATRON=1,
    WITH_MODULES=1, WITH_ZLIB=1

